    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carcerem 是一款第一人称的真实恐怖游戏。踏入古老迷宫的阴森走廊，深处传来恐怖的咆哮声和似乎是囚徒尖叫的回响。探索迷宫，揭开它的秘密——越深入，危险越大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245150/extras/af95d7798488219c36dec72acfa9f168.poster.avif?t=1761621992\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245150/extras/af95d7798488219c36dec72acfa9f168.webm?t=1761621992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245150/extras/af95d7798488219c36dec72acfa9f168.mp4?t=1761621992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角因罪被流放至迷宫中。他得知，凡能逃出者将获得赦免，因此决心为自由而战，不惜一切代价。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这座迷宫是一座数百年前建成的石制监狱。成千上万的囚犯在几个世纪中穿行其中，但无人成功逃脱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245150/extras/efeef14b22531a86128da6a008a6fc77.poster.avif?t=1761621992\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245150/extras/efeef14b22531a86128da6a008a6fc77.webm?t=1761621992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245150/extras/efeef14b22531a86128da6a008a6fc77.mp4?t=1761621992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>玩法</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解谜。 古老而神秘的谜题需要囚徒的智慧与机敏。关于它们的构造，人们一无所知。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找物品与线索。 对囚徒来说，没有什么比找到的物品或线索更宝贵。它们或许能帮助你前进，揭开迷宫的秘密。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >步步惊险。 在迷宫中无法放松，每一个转角都可能隐藏陷阱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245150/extras/5c26148f3169ed426ba3d178f19c763e.poster.avif?t=1761621992\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245150/extras/5c26148f3169ed426ba3d178f19c763e.webm?t=1761621992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245150/extras/5c26148f3169ed426ba3d178f19c763e.mp4?t=1761621992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>迷宫的秘密与传说</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能从迷宫中逃脱吗？没有人知道出口在哪里。你必须亲自揭开真相。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那些来自深处的咆哮传闻是真的吗？是什么生物守护着这座迷宫？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是否还有幸存者？若有，遇见他们将有多危险？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245150/extras/ae59b601aac5873bb0e633df57d898a4.poster.avif?t=1761621992\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245150/extras/ae59b601aac5873bb0e633df57d898a4.webm?t=1761621992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245150/extras/ae59b601aac5873bb0e633df57d898a4.mp4?t=1761621992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
